WEBVTT

00:00:01.490 --> 00:00:05.327
First task: Reconnaissance.
I want to know everything that's going on...

00:00:05.386 --> 00:00:08.414
in all three casinos,
from the rotation of the dealers...

00:00:08.622 --> 00:00:11.848
to the path of every cash cart.
I want to know everything about

00:00:11.874 --> 00:00:15.045
every guard, every watcher,
anyone with a security pass.

